title: The Fugitive S02E24 Everybody Gets Hit In The Mouth Sometime Div
description:
The Fugitive
S02E24
Everybody Gets Hit In The Mouth Sometime


    * One of 15 episodes from Season Two which have not been released on DVD
    * Remastered audio and video from VHS
    * Original music, not a synthesized replacement track


Airdate: March 9, 1965

Kimble becomes involved in the plight of Gus Hendrick (Jack Klugman), a debt-ridden trucker who continues to support his late partner's family.
Lucia: Geraldine Brooks. Kimble: David Janssen. Logan: G.B. Atwater. Ernie: Michael Constantine.
